  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients consulting in the Allergy Unit of the Arnaud de Villeneuve Hospital for whatever
      suspicion of allergy were asked to participate in the study. Besides a standard battery of
      respiratory allergens, native raw and cooked potato were tested by means of the prick to
      prick method, using a metal lancet.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
